   *     // limit multiple gestures.
   *     // See the explanation in {@link Interactable.draggable} example
   *     max: Infinity,
   *     maxPerElement: 1,
   * })
   *
   * var isGestureable = interact(element).gesturable()
   * ```
   *
   * Gets or sets whether multitouch gestures can be performed on the target
